cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the optimization of antenna arrays for network level performance, which falls under the category of Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networked Systems (cs.NI). The use of Machine Learning (cs.AI) and the proposed framework for optimization also suggest the categories of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Multimedia (cs.MM).
